{"tid":275571,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果斯爾馬在阿根廷出世，佢既日記會是咁的","createTime":"2017-06-08T06:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T06:36:26.000Z","uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25447b34043e4fa94c2f904fb530e04ba12a1279","tid":275571,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"1996年5月14日<br />\n今天爸爸買了一本日記薄給我，真的很開心！以後要好好記下我的事情。下課後和朋友們去了球場踢球，進了十多球！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不知道為什麼他們都追不上我。"},{"pid":"fa5e25efd25958e616bec80962a808a8efd66bfa","tid":275571,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a173b57058da6d1c2dfea3366ffb0bb18793c97","tid":275571,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"由於學緊西班牙文寫阿根廷斯爾馬既日記，暫時唔得閒，星期二我會繼續出文"},{"pid":"68f7394a2f02c5d57b6d5cdcf82df6aed019b006","tid":275571,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"樓主冇事 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a582d118550fdcd4080c49b3c630527c78ebd59c","tid":275571,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"🇹🇭👺🎭🇧🇷"},{"pid":"64c9edbcc2b0eb33a691766e4680a339732d3f4c","tid":275571,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>🇹🇭👺🎭🇧🇷</blockquote><br />\n吾係我尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8971488d866a2e7bffa55245d07d1d1f6863a200","tid":275571,"uid":82304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>🇹🇭👺🎭🇧🇷</blockquote><br />\n吾係我尼<img src=\"/assets/